ive/my-chemical-romance-los-angeles-reunion-gig-review-setlist-watch-2590495">于 2019 年 12 月首次重聚</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-deeply-sad-postpone-2021-tour-dates-2022-2922445">他们因新冠疫情而推迟的世界巡演</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-debut-new-music-and-rarities-at-first-uk-show-in-11-years-3226970">于去年夏天在康沃尔郡的 The Eden Project 举行了两场演出</a>。</p><p> <i>《NME》</i> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/my-chemical-romance-new-song-the-foundations-of-decay-3224859">在对《The Foundations of Decay》的四星评论中</a>写道：“My Chemical Romance 一直是一支重要且有影响力的乐队，他们的歌曲充满了与世隔绝、绝望和孤独的气息，并带有一种挑衅的乐观态度。”</p><p> “在他们的间歇期，”它补充道，“随着新一代粉丝发现他们和他们的信息，这种崇敬之情只会与日俱增。新音乐总是会带来风险，但《Foundations Of Decay》听起来从来不会陷入传统音乐的泥沼。赛道另一边，我的化学浪漫以美好、无所畏惧的形式回归，充满了火焰、紧迫感和充足的欢乐。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-fans-think-theyve-spotted-a-teaser-for-bands-new-album-3526984">关于 My Chemical Romance 新专辑被揭穿的谣言</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
朴恩彬为《Castaway Diva》配乐推出新歌《Someday》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/park-eun-bin-drops-new-song-someday-for-the-soundtrack-of-castaway-diva-3527682?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=park-恩彬为《漂流女主角》的原声带放弃了新歌Carmen ChinWed, 01 Nov 2023 09:35:10 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3527682 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="朴恩彬 漂流女主角 非凡律师吴" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这部韩剧的前两集于上周末首播后发布</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/park-eun-bin-drops-new-song-someday-for-the-soundtrack-of-castaway-diva-3527682">朴恩斌为《Castaway Diva》原声带推出的新歌《Someday》</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次亮相。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="朴恩彬 漂流女主角 非凡律师吴" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/park-eun-bin-diva-of-the-deserted-island-confirmed-lead-romcom-k-drama-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>女演员朴恩彬推出了一首名为“Someday”的全新歌曲，作为新韩剧《 <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/castaway-diva">Castaway Diva》</a>原声带的一部分。</em></p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/doona-review-emotionally-visceral-refreshingly-grounded-love-story-3520270">“杜娜！”评论：一个情感发自内心、令人耳目一新的爱情故事</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌于昨天（10 月 31 日）在音乐流媒体平台上发布，并附有其随附的音乐视频。该剪辑采用了取自该剧的情感场景蒙太奇，记录了主角木河（朴恩彬饰）被困在荒岛上以及她随后重新融入现代社会的故事。</p><p> 《Someday》的发行标志着朴槿惠迄今为止第二次发行音乐，此前她为<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/extraordinary-attorney-woo">《杰出律师吴宇森》</a></em>的配乐《济州岛的蓝色之夜》做出了贡献。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[MV] PARK EUN BIN(박은빈) _ Someday (CASTAWAY DIVA(무인도의 디바) OST 서목하 (박은빈) Vol.1)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2ugJDyef0sU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <i>《漂流女主角》</i>于 10 月 28 日首播，讲述了徐木河 (Seo Mok-ha) 的故事，她是一个粗鲁的乡村女孩，梦想成为一名流行歌星。在决定命运的一天，当莫哈前往首尔市实现梦想时，她不知何故发现自己被困在一座无人岛上，并在那里度过了接下来的 15 年。</p><p>朴恩彬去年因在 Netflix 的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/extraordinary-attorney-woo">《非常律师吴》</a></em>中饰演 Mok-ha 而获得主流知名度，她在剧中饰演 Mok-ha，其他演员包括 Kim Hyo-jin、Chae Jong-hyeop、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vixx">VIXX 的</a>N（饰演 Cha）等。学妍）等等。</p><p>剧集将于韩国标准时间每周六和周日晚上 9:20 在韩国有线电视网络 tvN 播出。流媒体平台 Netflix 将以与 tvN 一致的上映时间表将该剧带给全球观众。</p><p>去年，朴恩斌主演了热门韩剧<em>《吴律师》</em> 。 <em>NME</em>将该剧列入<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/features/tv-features/nme-best-korean-dramas-kdramas-series-of-the-year-2022-3368751">2022 年 10 部最佳韩剧</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/features/tv-features/nme-best-asian-tv-shows-of-the-year-2022-3368839">2022 年 10 部最佳亚洲电视节目</a>名单。</p><p>与此同时， <em>《吴特级律师》</em>的制作公司最近证实，已与剧集编剧文智媛签署了<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/tv/extraordinary-attorney-woo-season-two-officially-in-the-works-3454608">制作这部热门韩剧第二季的</a>合同。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/park-eun-bin-drops-new-song-someday-for-the-soundtrack-of-castaway-diva-3527682">朴恩斌为《Castaway Diva》原声带推出的新歌《Someday》</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次亮相。</p> ;
