izzo">利佐 (Lizzo)</a>则以纪念已故蒂娜·特纳 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tina-turner">Tina Turner)</a>的造型来庆祝万圣节，同时也扮演了 1988 年电影<em>《黑暗情妇埃尔维拉》中的埃尔维拉 (Elvira)。</em> 。</p><p>海蒂·克拉姆 (Heidi Klum) 凭借她的孔雀装无疑抢尽了风头，旁边的 10 名表演者为她打造了色彩缤纷的翅膀套装。 </p><figure id="attachment_3527677" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3527677" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3527677" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/heidi-klum-peacock-halloween-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="海蒂·克鲁姆 (Heidi Klum) 装扮成孔雀参加 2023 年万圣节" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/heidi-klum-peacock-halloween-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/heidi-klum-peacock-halloween-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/heidi-klum-peacock-halloween-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/heidi-klum-peacock-halloween-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/heidi-klum-peacock-halloween-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/heidi-klum-peacock-halloween-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3527677" class="wp-caption-text">海蒂·克拉姆 (Heidi Klum) 演绎 2023 年万圣节。图片来源：Udo Salters/Patrick McMullan via Getty Images </figcaption></figure><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cy-PeVSObuS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; fl