 ARTMS 的 HeeJin 透露，自从出道以来，她还没有“交过名人朋友” https://www.nme.com/news/music/artms-heejin-reveals-she-hasnt-made-celebrity-friends-since-her-debut-3527652?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=artms-heejin-reveals-自从出道以来，她还没有交过名人朋友Carmen ChinWed, 01 Nov 2023 07:31:51 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3527652 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="loona artms heejin 名人好友采访" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手称这是“常见的误解”</p><p> ARTMS 的 HeeJin 透露，自从首次亮相<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artms-heejin-reveals-she-hasnt-made-celebrity-friends-since-her-debut-3527652">以来，她还没有“交过名人朋友”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="loona artms heejin 名人好友采访" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/loona-artms-heejin-celebrity-friends-interview-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/artms">ARTMS</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/heejin">HeeJin</a>公开了她作为公众人物在社交方面面临的困难。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/loossemble-review-charming-re-introduction-3501635">Loossemble –“Loossemble”评论：迷人的重新介绍</a></strong></li></ul><p>HeeJin 最近接受了<em><a href="https://www.vanityteen.com/heejin-digital-cover/" target="”_blank”" rel="noopener">《Vanity Teen</a> 》最新数字封面的采访，</em>她在采访中坦率地谈到了她和其他韩国名人在组建社交圈时面临的挑战。</p><p> “人们普遍误解，成为偶像就会拥有很多名人朋友，但这实际上相当具有挑战性，”这位 ARTMS 歌手告诉媒体。</p><p>她后来透露，尽管她在2016年出道，但即使是现在，她也很少有名人朋友。“也许是因为我的性格，但我认为自从我作为偶像出道以来，我就没有交过名人朋友，”她补充道。</p><p>在采访的其他地方，HeeJin 还谈到了 ARTMS 即将推出的音乐。该团体由 LOONA 的五位成员组成，分别是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kim-lip">Kim Lip</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/choerry">Choerry</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jinsoul">Jinsoul</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/haseul">Haseul</a>和 HeeJin 本人。</p><p>这位歌手透露，该乐队目前“正在计划阶段”有一些事情。 “我可以说 ARTMS 明年将带着一张精彩的专辑回归，就像封印已经被打破一样，”她补充道。</p><p>昨天（10月31日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artms-heejin-pays-tribute-to-korean-culture-in-algorithm-music-video-3526546">熙珍携首张迷你专辑《K》以solo歌手身份回归</a>。这张唱片以主打歌《Algorithm》为主打，这是她自 2016 年发行同名单曲以来的首张个人发行专辑，该单曲在她作为 LOONA 成员首次亮相之前就已发行。</p><p> 7月，她的ARTMS乐队成员和LOONA小队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/odd-eye-circle">Odd Eye Circle</a>带着<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/odd-eye-circle-new-beginnings-more-freedom-loona-version-up-interview-3467710">迷你专辑“Version Up”</a>回归。这张专辑是在成员们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/loona-heejin-kim-lip-jinsoul-choerry-terminate-contract-blockberry-creative-3381192">去年因公开诉讼离开 Blockberry Creative</a>后与 Jaden Jeong 领导的 Modhaus 签约后发行的。</p><p>在其他韩国流行音乐新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jessi-describes-her-viral-hit-zoom-as-an-annoying-ass-song-3526509">韩裔美国说唱歌手 Jessi</a>在最近出现在<em>Zach Sang Show 中时，将她 2022 年火爆的歌曲《Zoom》描述为一首“烦人的屁股歌曲”。</em></p><p>她说这首歌被“过度播放”了，然后在录制完这首歌后告诉主持人扎克·桑她对这首歌的想法：“我无意中听到了自己的声音，我当时想，‘该死的，我很烦人’。”</p><p> ARTMS 的 HeeJin 透露，自从首次亮相<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artms-heejin-reveals-she-hasnt-made-celebrity-friends-since-her-debut-3527652">以来，她还没有“交过名人朋友”</a> 。</p> ;
